so..i get a phone call from my mom who is missing and says shes in Penn. Why I ask? Cuz my uncle is dying wiht brain cancer. So after i pick myself up off the floor. She explains hown i have to go there and say my goodbyes. Saying he has about 3 years to live, and thats if he makes it through the surgery. So I go there to say goodbye to my 24 year old uncle. And thats where I have been the past couple of days. BUt good news!hes not dead. and he made it. and its cancer but not too bad of cancer.Its treatable.they say 3-5 years i think he can go longer. im just trying to be happy here.

im sad. I'm lonely. and my uncle just told me some stuff i realized. alot of things i messed up. Alot of things i wish i could fix. And i go through this about once a year. But its so different this time. like..my life..had explanations to it.finally.all those bumps in the road really did change everything.and that its okay to make mistakes.the only thing that sucks is i made alot of big ones.or maybe just one reallll big one.and i wish i could fix it.
I <3 my uncle eric...forever

road test the 23rd omg!aaa
sept. 2nd first day of Med. school.

well...i figure ill write something else in here being as there has only been bull shit the past few posts.Being thats what you get for having a journal and jealous people.They jsut dont mix i guess. anyways...My spanish final is in 2 and a half hours and i need to do alot of stuff.lol but i dont have a poster board.umm its been an interesting week.  I failed my road test but we wont go there, heh =( and daryll broke his hand and i sat in teh hospital for hours yesterday and then dinenr with dad and family. Keeping in touch with alot of people lately. Good shit. Chilled with Jeaninne and John and went out to eat for the goodbye party. Prom and graduation is in almost a week hehe.yessss!!!my poor dress needs to be hemed and takin in.hell yea weight watchers!i dunno thats it..journal bores me now.

that I am so nice to everyone. I havent had a problemw ith anyone since the 9th grade. This is ridiculous. I am pathetic but yet you find my journal, read it and then comment. I only have one friend?I'm sorry to say I cant party all the time wtih one friend.pick a story and stick to it. I am not a bitch to anyone or atleast i try not to be. I have my own problems that you have no business being in.Go get your own life and stop being so jealous of mine.Cuz you know what?You know where ill be when your eating out of the garbage?In med school with a long relationship and the bestest friend in the world having fun not fucking with people. My boyfriend might not be the best in your eyes but that doesnt matter to me. In 4 years I have not gave a shit what anyone has thought of him.High school is over for me. Stop the dumb high school bull shit I dont want it anymore.So either tell me who you are or fucking stop. I didnt do shit to you.

listen..this is my venting area to make me feel better.If anyone doesnt like the posts please stop reading them. And I refuse to ahve anymore nasty comments in here.ANything else thats needing to be said,talk to me.stop writting your crap in here like that.I'm done.

How about this is my journal..MY journal. I can write what I want...but I wont listen to your bull shit.So do me a favor and don't write your crap in here anymore..thanks for the drama..lol and by the way...before you go accusing people of bull shit why dont you ask them first rather then writting in their journal..thats real bold.oo and I believe it was you just now flipping a shit,not me. and I guess I flipped such a shit that I hung out with you that day.controlling?HAHA!you just think(not bill) that all the people I hang out with are your friends too.And thats not even the topic at hand.But.....WHY DONT YA MAKE A BIGGER DEAL ABOUT SOME NONSENSE PLEASE!i love how you fucking confront me about this bull shit in here.very nice
people can be so inconciderate I swear. Either that or completly brain dead. I don't do this to you. BUt you do this EVERYTIME!I <3 good friends =/

Venting poetry: All I have to say is I miss YOU! And when I'm laying here thinking,it's always about YOU!And when you see me crying, know it's also about YOU! No matter how far I travel or how endless the day, I can't stop wondering how we let it get this way.And when I feel like dying, and I'm at my worst..there you are, just your image..to save my soul. I love you more then you know, more then can you feel..I thought it was just something I ought to tell you.

~loving you is like breathing, you do it unknowingly,you need it to live, and its what lets you live day to day.

A few questions that I need to know
How you could ever hurt me so
I need to know, what I've done wrong
And how long it's been going on
Was it that I never paid enough attention?
Or did I not give enough affection?
Not only will your answers keep me sane
But I'll know never to make the same mistake again

You can tell me to my face,
Or even on the phone,
You can write it in a letter,
Either way, I have to know
Did I never treat you right?
Did I always start the fight?
Either way I'm going out of my mind
All the answers to my questions, I have to find

I'm just waiting
Cos' I heard that this feelin wont last that long

Never ever have I ever felt so low
When you gonna take me out of this black hole
Never ever have I ever felt so sad
The way I'm feelin yeah, you got me feelin really bad
Never ever have I had to find
I've had to dig away to find my own peace of mind
I've never ever had my conscious to fight
The way I'm feelin' yeah, it just dont feel right

I'm a ways along..but yet so scared.
Alot more scaed then most poeple I've met.
I dont wanna do it i just dont.
no way around it, i'm so scared.
not coming throught this door anymore.
not having the back support a bedroom door away.
a completly new life.
i'm so scared.
I never thought this actually happened.
I lived in never never land.
I'm so scared.
I dont wanna grow up..
I've moved my life much too fast.
I'm sos cared, I really dont think I can make it.
I dont wanna grow up...

I'm wearing so thin right now.  My patience,my happiness of everything is wearing thin. I have to pray to get into these radiology schools,pass my road test,pass chem regents,focus on keeping my job 4 days a week, prom and EVERYTHIGN else. I feel so hectic right now and all your doing is making it worse.  All you can think about is yourself. You probably have no idea what's even goign on in my life cuz you don't remember anything I say. And why is that?CUZ YOU DONT HEAR ANYTHING I SAY. You have no idea how good you have it right now. Not a clue in the world. You life is based on just you. I've done some fucked up shit in the past but thats the whole point of growing up. You figure shit out.  I can't take the way you talk to me anymore and how you see life. I can't understand why you're so angry at everything esspecially me. I won't ever get the fact of how you can be with someone for long and still not have a clue of what love is. Cuz if you did you wouldn't wanna toss it aside everyday like it was a penny. I'm a person not an item and I deserve the same treatment that you give yourself. I deseve to go to movies and dinners ALONE and I deserve to have picnics and have doors opened and coats handed to me. Thats whats makes me the girlfriend and your the boyfriend. This is one of your 3 responsibities in life right now and you can't seem to do it. HOw hard is it to see the goodness in people?Why always the bad? I dont understand you and perhaps I never will but why let that happen? Why won't you stop doing this to anyone close to you. Is cuz you hurt therefore I should?But why do you hurt?Why cant I ever do a good job in helping?Why don't you understand me?WHY DON'T I GET IT!?how can you say you love me and then call me all these things.Why do you like being unhappy? You can never accept blame for anything that you do. You can only bring shit up from the past to try and make me look like the bad guy. I see right through you but I haven't done anything wrong to you in a long time. And you have done some pretty hefty things too. It's time to either forgive and forget..or forget me. Cuz I can't live like this anymore. I need to focus on my future.I want you there but with a smile on your face waiting for me,a girl you love. Not me the girl you vent on.I'm me take it or leave it..if you wanna take it,prove it.

Some new things going on lately.I have my new job with Lauren which is alot of fun hehe. Damnit greg where the fuck is my check?lol fashion show is tomorrow. I wanna go but plans got changed and some peoples got called into work. Doesnt look like daryll and I are going to Conn. on Sunday. He has a show to play though in replace of Conn. so that should be fun.My dog goes for walks without a leash..I'm proud =)I'm digustingly tired lately. Drivers ed is going well but the girls in my car are so retarded. umm The after prom thing is a go. Just need to get all the money and purchase tickets =) hmm what else is new?Gotta plan out bills which is must do.okay now for my rant being as I'm tired of just updating in here and not voicing my feelings hehe =)

Now here's the confuzzled part. I dunno, I just..ugh..Have you ever just felt like you're putting everythinggggg in and it just never seems to get better. Even flat out saying to the other person it takes 2 and I love you but I need some love back from you, and it just never happens? Whats with that? I'm just so confused on what to do right now. How to fix things. everyday its something new,something that is said to make me feel more empty.Or something not said to make me feel more empty. I dunno whether to be angry upset, dissipointed, scared...all of em?I just dont know what to feel or say anymore.Maybe I'm just crazy..


"The intoxication of anger, like that of the grape, shows us to others, but hides us from ourselves"

I must have forgot I had this thing for alittle bit. Well..whats new?lemme think. Umm I took that test I passed with flying colors and i did the interview which went every well. BUt 125 people are applying and only 25 will get in. The first to get in are the ones who applied for it last year. So I'm a lil screwed.BUt its all good.I'm tired of stressing.  Next week starts vacation and also my 2nd choice college interview.Which I'm not nervous about at all. Chem can still suck me. April Y me had a terrible time at the spanish thing,muy aburrido. Ummmm Suppose to be staying at bills for a night over vacation,gotta work out those plans heh.I'm glad play is over,kinda broke my heart at the end.Daryll and I are doing better. I just wish he gave out a little more affection then he does. I feel like I put everything in and he just sits there and goes about his own life. I can only do so much. Anyways..sat. april and I and some wierd crew went to applebees for a bite to eat around 1am. Kinda went a lil wrong,do to some people being there that made it difficult to have fun. On top of being destroyed dealing with alot of crap lol.hmm what else?I start my new job today I believe unless this snow keeps up.Then tomorrow. I'm kinda excited to be working with my friends and stuff. Makes things easier to adapt to,I guess. I loved working with april but fratellis is a bull shit job and she'll realize that when she leaves.Well I've babbled enough.so.....what are YOU thinking about?

Some crazy ass shit has been going on lol.Ask April hehe. My biggest test is tomorrow. God I'm nervous. Tonight is Dawsons creek I havent seen that show in a mad long time lol. Chem is ridiculous.Fuck it.  And April and I are going on a Spanish trip to teach origami..if I only knew how lol. And tend the soda stand lol.So talented.Prom dresses and Prom after math and Graduation party..so much setting up to do.So much planning. I didn't get accepted to Mercy medical center. I dunno if I wrote about that yet. BUt it sucks,but it wasnt a heartbreaker.It was my last choice. Now if that were South Nassau I'd cry,literally. Well gunna do the work out and shower thing.Fucking stomach.

What an awesome feeling waking up today. The heat was on too high so I woke up every hour and talked to my mom at 5am for awhile. I put on shorts and a tank top.  And when I woke up it was almost 1:15. But it was sunny and I was in little clothes. IT WAS SUMMER to me.God I miss the summer.I havent been sleeping well(what else is new) and it felt nice to sleep.No one was here or anything. It was such a great feeling.

Today...I dunno what the deal is yet.All I know is I'm not happy about going to school tomorrow. I can't wait till the break in April. I asked my parents about that whole thing Bill(if you read this) It's cool..I'll stay for however long.

Well I'm gunna go work out so I can take my shower soon. And get out and play in the beautiful day

Way too many carrots in their sauce.I can't belive this weekend went by so fast. It was amazing how fast it went by.I talked on the phone with Bill todya for just about 5 hours hehe. Vented and just conversated.. =)I'm looking for some new hamster cages.  For the lil' guy.Well...Goodnight

I dont wanna bore john ya know?....

Well today I realized I was fat...Like I've known im chunky but today I felt fat. I've been working out just about all day.  Taking breaks alot...but none the less working out. I ate alot fo healthy foods until dinner..I had 2 biscuits.hmmm bad me.

I napped today and got alot of sleep alst night but I feel mad tired still.I guess from using alot of energy. AIM is being a cock right now.damnit.

I saw my wife today.We hung out =) I got a new skirt and AWESOME shirt yesterday at the mall with abrilla. THANK YOU ABRILLA!!!!!!!!!!!!

Shower time...cya

This update is just for you Madonia.

Well me and abrilla have been doing alot of fun things ;) everday this week. I cant wait for her to get home from detention.  The talent show last week was pretty good.I got to spend time with a few people I normally don't that was a bonus.  School is okay I guess. I'm kinda getting in the slacking mode.  But for me slacking is like 85's. I'm just tired of everything.

I missed rehearsal yesterday due to sickness and term paper issues and then I went out from 10-12 to see Daryll. Which was quite possibly the best idea I've ever had...or he had. Either or.

Pepe abrilla dn I are doing"Danny and the dinosuar" for spanish =) I love that book.Abrilla and I had a good sandwich yesterday and some popcorn mom made us.  My cat loves to attack printers.Random....

Tomorrow is drivers ed again and then friday too since we had a snow day.  Kinda bull shit if you ask me...

All in all I'm doing pretty awesome.  Daryll and I are wroking things out pretty smoothly and I love him. Arpil and I are now offically married.  Look at our ring fingers =) we're branded lol..today her and I are gunna make it another girls nnight/day and just chill and ameba as usual lol...

Okay Madonia I will update later on when I ahve more news...I AM NOW NAPPING MY HEAD OFF

The sky was so so last night...way too many clouds..but the feeling was still there....Drivers ed again today. I guess I can't make rehearsal unless I got late.reallllllly late lol. Talent show tomorrow..I wont get my hopes up too high for it though. I gotta stay the whole damn time tho lol.

As for this bullshit with 'the worst group ever' i'm just gunna drop it. Some kids are too lil for me to care about. I mean... I chill in parking lots with someone at the same time I was leaving my house to go to my brothers wrestling adn rehearsal. And he didnt even have rehearsal.yup.  It's funny how more then one person hears this. LoL high school is a load of bull shit. Thank God for the J.Crew lol. Thank God for April and for people that dont flip out LoL.

Past week or so has been an odd one. A good and bad at the same time. School...theres just too fucking much to do. ROUGH with all this work heh

Jeaninne has surgery today I hope all is well. She should be coming with me and John tomorrow for the talent show.  Oh eya The Used was on the radio...hmmmm can't wait to go.

After I left school today at 12 and dropped my wife off since she wasn't feeling well..me and dad bonded and got lunch and stuff. I got a BLT which I have been craving for a mad long time now. I was happy. Tomorrow dad said Charlies Hot dog truck at 12 =) All in all I'm pretty okay nowa days

I like being on good terms with the mant people I fixed thing with. I'm happy for me =)

In which I planned already lol.  And for you people that love to lie..about parking lots. Real fucking cool. grow up. I was never in any parking lot LMAO and for that matter sorry brian for the confusion that people made. Not my fault.=) end of story on that.  But however I would like to say that I laughed my ass off with along with April.Very amusing.. Mad funny thank you =) now proceed to stay out of my life lil' ones.

Before you read this know you cant post a comment and tell what you feel,being secret or not,just read before you judge:  I'm pulling my hair out wondering why you're all the way over there and I'm here. Wondering how in the hell we let it get this far and how you couldn't care. It's been so long since we've even enchanged words.I'm not asking for a ton of things from you.  I'm asking you to just pop in and say 'hi'.  It's this part of the year that is making it rough none the less. And there's so much I could say to you and put in here. But it's so pointless if it's not to your face. I bet you have an idea that I'm talking to you now. But you couldn't careless.  This isn't me attacking you saying you're a bad person.
